Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Situated Close to Russell Defence Office

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Campbell 5 is a prime mixed use development comprised of 4 premium towers which have been inspired by great cities across the world. 

Situated 1.3 kilometers from the Canberra CBD and within proximity to Russell Defence Offices, Campbell 5 offers a unique opportunity to start your services based business in a strategic location on the Parliamentary axis of Constitution Avenue and Anzac Parade. 

Available now to purchase or lease, the 3 individual office spaces looking over award winning Hassett Park all come with dedicated car parking. 

Suite 1: 202sqm* with 3 spaces - Under offer
Suite 2: 282sqm* with 4 spaces - Sold
Suite 3: 301sqm* with 3 spaces

*Approx.

Please contact your exclusive CBRE Agents for an Information Memorandum and to organise an inspection.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BOUTIQUE OFFICE SPACES IN CAMPBELL 5 PRECINCT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Campbell 5 is one of Canberra's premium new precincts situated in the Inner North.  The area will benefit from a influx of residents and a mix of various commercial offerings offering a variety of amenity to the area.  

Available for lease is a retail suite suitable for a restaurant, cafe, professional office or professional services operator.  Unit G31 features the following;
- 109sqm*
- Ready for fit out
- Provisions for Air conditoining
- Provisions for Grease Trap and Exhaust
- Excellent street presence
- 1x basement car space
- NBN Ready
- Common bathrooms
- Street parking at the units door step

Do not miss out on this opportunity to be part of this exciting new precinct.  For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

The fitout comprises;
